name: Mecha Foodzilla
description:
Still around the world of the metaverse in the steven spielberg movie about the meta world "Ready player one"!. yes yes yes!... Indukayam wants to be mecha godzilla, because he believes that godzilla or t-rex is Roosters ancestor.
but, suddenly he feels hungry. So, the metaverse granted his wish. He becomes a Mecha Foodzilla. And his Chicken Leg weapon Stick transform into...Hello, do you want ice cream? LOL
